title: 雕漆隐花，雕出紫气东来！Carved lacquer with hidden flowers, carrying auspiciousness!丨Liziqi Channel
description:
Please  subscribe to 【李子柒 Liziqi 】Liziqi Channel on YouTube if you like my videos: https://goo.gl/nkjpSx 
#李子柒#Liziqi#lýtửthất#ChineseCuisine #chineseculture #lacquer #lacquerware 

This lacquer video is four years late.​
The Chinese pronunciation of lacquer is the same as "qi",​
I named this lacquerware hidden flowers "Zi Qi Dong Lai (the coming auspiciousness)",​
Kylin looks back and wipes away all the sorrow.​
I send this wish to everyone who sees the video, I miss you very much.
这个大漆视频迟到了四年
“漆”同“柒”
我给这幅雕漆隐花的漆器作品取名“紫气东来”
麒麟回首，万事不愁
也把这份祝愿送给看到视频的每一个你，很想你们
